eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A REQUIRED WEEKLY TEST FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Olmsted, MN; AT 06:42 AM ON SEP 19, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 07:42 AM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: Rochester Emergency Management is conducting a test of the Emergency Alert System for the city of Rochester.  If this was a real emergency, instructions would follow with steps to take for personal safety.  This is only a test.
